Accepting defaults to questions asked appears to be fine.
Upload generated key (/boot/home/config/settiongs/ssh/id_rsa.pub) to Gerrit: https://review.haiku-os.org/settings/#SSHKeys

Verify SSH is running via: eval ‘ssh-agent -s’
Add key to SSH: ssh-add /boot/home/config/settings/ssh/id_rsa

Change directory into 'haiku' folder that was downloaded from github earlier

Verify git connection: 'git remote -v'
